title.rendered: LPN – Women’s Health Care | Tulsa, OK

content.rendered:
LPN – Women’s Health Care | Tulsa, Oklahoma
  • Full time Monday-Friday 8am-5pm
  • Candidate must have a good work history
  • Will assist the physician during clinic hours with Obstetric and Gynecological care
  • Prefer LPN with OB/Gyn or Women’s Health experience
  • Must have 1-2 years’ working experience as an LPN in a clinic or hospital
  • BLS required, ACLS preferred
  • Current Oklahoma LPN license
  • $15-$18/hour
